Name: Language Sharing Interface
Article:
The purpose for this development is to create a tool supporting transcription work. There are following objectives:
• Aligning Indigenous spoken language materials such as words or parts of speech to for combinations of generated syllables from collected recordings and people’s new voice recordings.
• Provide suitable interactive interface for support for the collecting work between non-Indigenous and Indigenous speaker.
